Package car_simulator

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Car
    This class is set up to implement the abstract class of Vehicle.
    Config
    Class for containing some setting variables, if any.
    Point
    A simple class of a point, which here is the location in which the car could be positioned.
    ResultTracker
    Class for keeping track of the results of a simulation.
    Room
    Function for setting up the room in which the Car will be doing the simulation.
    Simulator
    Class for setting up the simulation environment specified in the assignment.
    Vehicle
    The abstract class show-casing what needs to be implemented.
